{"tid":174243,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖] 依家d 90後返工恰眼瞓！你袋緊人工架！","createTime":"2017-03-26T15:57:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-27T01:31:42.000Z","uid":59700,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"955b272ec35029d7f81f554dc3be603e54b9f210","tid":174243,"uid":59700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T15:57:46.000Z","msg":"今日老細就有個好重要既演講，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講到明要執到靚仔靚女，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n老細演講就係後面充撑下場面就得，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知有隻90後，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢就啱啱先入職，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今日上到台上面，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n隻90後竟然當住眾人面前恰眼瞓！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n示意圖：<br />\n我地：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老細：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n90後：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁多人睇住都夠膽恰眼瞓，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n老細去返後台塊面又黑又西，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我就即刻鬧到佢差d cry，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢話今日星期日，要咁早起身返工好辛苦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依家d 90後明知第二日返工就早啲訓啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n企下做佈景版都要恰眼瞓！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"836485608dfa3eae436b1c241c3d4541b90a605c","tid":174243,"uid":94568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T16:06:05.000Z","msg":"有圖＝無圖"},{"pid":"3f79cbfebda41ad1c5d87889f5fcccefe5083517","tid":174243,"uid":60256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T16:14:32.000Z","msg":"而家啲90後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb103a5a4c1e4df08a33465b4746fc2133097e8c","tid":174243,"uid":9328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T16:16:48.000Z","msg":"咪係！老細同人地connect 緊嫁嘛，容乜易俾佢搞到disconnect"},{"pid":"23b6be1862240ca7ef0673d54dfc953cea7f4a72","tid":174243,"uid":14716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T16:21:04.000Z","msg":"以為林鄭個學生妹妹張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3e44222f6a0084a51f4f4fd049677bdbd74ad30","tid":174243,"uid":94452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T16:23:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以為林鄭個學生妹妹張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2k12WgN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2k12WgN.jpg&h=566b7809&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b22e8eaffd1e5850d236ea40908e4a291a644d61","tid":174243,"uid":59700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T16:28:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>以為林鄭個學生妹妹張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad